Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.91,0:02:31.59,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}挫けない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.91,0:02:31.59,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}也不會氣餒
